{"type":null,"faqId":10021,"title":"G6-U00邮箱设置","answer":"<p style=\"text-indent:-12.2pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span><span>（--</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>添加<span>Email</span>帐户<span> </span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>在主屏幕，点击<b>电子邮件</b>。登陆账号分为手动设置和自动设置。<span></span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">-- </span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">手动设置：<span></span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>1.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>账户设置界面<span>-&gt;</span>输入账号和密码。<span></span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>2.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>点击手动设置。<span></span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>3.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>点击<span>POP3</span>，进入接收服务器设置界面。<span></span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>4.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>点击下一步，进入外发服务器设置界面。<span></span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>5.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>点击下一步，进入邮件接收设置界面，可选择收件箱检查频率。<span></span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>6.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>点击下一步，进入设置电子邮件界面为此账户创建名称和您的姓名。<span></span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>7.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><